{"tid":2189202,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★解放軍直升機朝九晚九操練 　元朗街坊WFH叫苦連天","createTime":"2020-09-04T17:05:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T08:23:33.000Z","uid":19454,"like":61,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a941c9b629d43f244fb778445b9c8fb9155b4914","tid":2189202,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T17:05:18.000Z","msg":"元朗區議會周二（1日）討論「解放軍駐港部隊直升機噪音及安全」。區議員林廷衞指，駐軍直升機經常「低飛」，直升機與采葉庭及映御屋苑只有百多米距離，曾有街坊投訴直升機噪音令她心跳加快，憂慮住宅安全。而席間錦銹區議員杜嘉倫亦指，噪音甚至趕走看樓盤的市民。他表示，香港人最怕樓價跌，但曾有市民在錦銹花園看樓盤期間，因聽到直升機巨響，而<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>立即放棄看該樓盤。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/18%E5%8D%80%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/519556/%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E8%BB%8D%E7%9B%B4%E5%8D%87%E6%A9%9F%E6%9C%9D%E4%B9%9D%E6%99%9A%E4%B9%9D%E6%93%8D%E7%B7%B4-%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E8%A1%97%E5%9D%8Awfh%E5%8F%AB%E8%8B%A6%E9%80%A3%E5%A4%A9-bb%E4%B8%8B%E6%99%9D%E7%9E%93%E5%94%94%E5%88%B0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F18%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F519556%2F%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E6%2594%25BE%25E8%25BB%258D%25E7%259B%25B4%25E5%258D%2587%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%259C%259D%25E4%25B9%259D%25E6%2599%259A%25E4%25B9%259D%25E6%2593%258D%25E7%25B7%25B4-%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E8%25A1%2597%25E5%259D%258Awfh%25E5%258F%25AB%25E8%258B%25A6%25E9%2580%25A3%25E5%25A4%25A9-bb%25E4%25B8%258B%25E6%2599%259D%25E7%259E%2593%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%2588%25B0&d=RlZLtXxvTyjhSejQ4AJs4wmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=8ac761a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/18%E5%8D%80%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/519556/%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E8%BB%8D%E7%9B%B4%E5%8D%87%E6%A9%9F%E6%9C%9D%E4%B9%9D%E6%99%9A%E4%B9%9D%E6%93%8D%E7%B7%B4-%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E8%A1%97%E5%9D%8Awfh%E5%8F%AB%E8%8B%A6%E9%80%A3%E5%A4%A9-bb%E4%B8%8B%E6%99%9D%E7%9E%93%E5%94%94%E5%88%B0</a>"},{"pid":"5aa3dc444a450e9df8d72dbd391bbd1d00d98159","tid":2189202,"uid":19454,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T17:05:34.000Z","msg":"駐軍周二至日操練 嬰兒難入眠<br />\n<br />\n疫情下不少街坊需要在家工作，但直升機常於下午3、4時為操練高峰期。林指，屋民反映噪音經常打斷他們工作。如有教師進行視像教學期間因噪音需停止教學，「真係等佢走咗先繼續」。他又指另有家長投訴，嬰兒下午因噪音難以入眠，照顧者更難抽空休息。<br />\n<br />\n路線忽略新樓宇落成 促重新制定訓練路線<br />\n<br />\n林廷衞解釋，駐軍的訓練路線忽略了新樓宇的高度。自2018年起跟進事件的他認為，近年元朗陸續有新屋苑落成，如接近駐軍訓練路線的映御屋苑為當時區內新屋苑。他建議解放軍應按區內發展重新制定訓練路線，遠離民居。"},{"pid":"d0e0396735d77d4653bb7db34db3244f111cef8f","tid":2189202,"uid":19454,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T17:07:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a2fe0d6383cb8dc72714e913fbb257d7c1a824d","tid":2189202,"uid":101945,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T17:15:04.000Z","msg":"一陣唔小心飛入屋擁抱業主<br />\n一齊見毛主席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8ebdd26a4bbc6e10ac93c44423c9bd502d90813","tid":2189202,"uid":334765,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T17:29:39.000Z","msg":"元朗國樓價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8be363f090d1af99b729474712a62f5bcfed226a","tid":2189202,"uid":19454,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"d8ebdd26a4bbc6e10ac93c44423c9bd502d90813","tid":2189202,"uid":334765,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T17:29:39.000Z","msg":"元朗國樓價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T17:43:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n8OZsX6.gif\" data-t